short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: If your Chrome opens Github pages too late or with multiple timeout errors, this extension will fix the problem.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
It keeps GitHub connection alive by sending a GET request for a small content on GitHub every 15 seconds.

Source code: https://github.com/gowhari/github-keep-alive
